---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const steps=[["01","创建","使用 Pi Extension API 定义运行时能力。"],["02","验证","在真实 Pi runtime 中验证工具、生命周期和边界。"],["03","打包","运行时代码、Skill 和可选 Web 资源由同一 package 拥有。"],["04","发布","交付一个来源、版本与权限说明都可验证的归档。"]];
---
<BaseLayout title="开发 Pi Extension — Pipee" description="使用 Pi Extension API 开发并交付可安装能力。"><div class="page"><section class="content-hero pad"><span class="eyebrow">Developers</span><div><h1>为 Pi 构建新的能力。</h1><p>你开发的是 Pi Extension。Pipee 只提供发现、安装说明和可选的 Web Surface，不创造第二套插件运行时。</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="button dark" href="/docs#first">创建第一个 Extension <span>→</span></a><a class="quiet-link" href="/requests">查看用户需求</a></div></div></section><section class="starter pad content-section"><div class="content-section-head"><span class="eyebrow">Start here</span><div><h2>最小的 Extension，<br/>就是一个 Pi 入口。</h2><p>先让运行时能力独立成立。只有确实需要可视化时，才增加 Pipee Web Surface。</p></div></div><div class="starter-grid"><div class="file-tree surface"><span class="mono-label">Package structure</span><pre>pi-hello/
├── src/
│   └── extension.ts
├── package.json
└── README.md</pre><div class="optional"><span>可选</span><code>dist/web/</code><small>仅在需要 Web Surface 时添加</small></div></div><div class="code-block"><header><span>src/extension.ts</span><span>Pi Extension</span></header><pre><span class="syntax">export default function</span> (pi: ExtensionAPI) &#123;
  pi.registerTool(&#123;
    name: <span class="string">"hello_pipee"</span>,
    description: <span class="string">"返回一个问候"</span>,
    parameters: Type.Object(&#123;&#125;),
    async execute() &#123;
      return &#123; content: [&#123; type: <span class="string">"text"</span>, text: <span class="string">"你好"</span> &#125;] &#125;
    &#125;
  &#125;)
&#125;</pre></div></div></section><section class="model pad content-section"><div class="content-section-head"><span class="eyebrow">Ownership</span><div><h2>一个运行时，两个清楚的层。</h2></div></div><div class="ownership surface"><div><span class="mono-label">Required</span><strong>Pi Extension</strong><p>工具、事件、状态、后台服务和生命周期。</p></div><div><span class="mono-label">Optional</span><strong>Pipee Web Surface</strong><p>当能力需要专属界面时，由同一 package 提供。</p></div></div></section><section class="delivery pad content-section"><div class="content-section-head"><span class="eyebrow">Delivery</span><div><h2>从代码到可安装归档。</h2></div></div><ol>{steps.map((step)=><li><span>{step[0]}</span><strong>{step[1]}</strong><p>{step[2]}</p></li>)}</ol><a class="button dark docs-link" href="/docs">阅读完整开发文档 <span>→</span></a></section></div></BaseLayout>
<style>.hero-actions{align-items:center;display:flex;gap:28px;margin-top:34px}.starter-grid{display:grid;gap:16px;grid-template-columns:.75fr 1.25fr}.file-tree{padding:25px}.file-tree pre{font:12px/2 var(--mono);margin:30px 0}.optional{border-top:1px solid var(--line);display:grid;gap:8px;padding-top:20px}.optional span{color:var(--blue);font:700 8px var(--mono);text-transform:uppercase}.optional code{font:700 11px var(--mono)}.optional small{color:var(--dim);font-size:10px}.model{background:#eeeeeb}.ownership{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.ownership>div{padding:30px}.ownership>div+div{border-left:1px solid var(--line)}.ownership strong{display:block;font-size:23px;margin-top:38px}.ownership p{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;line-height:1.75;margin:12px 0 0}.delivery ol{border-top:1px solid var(--ink);display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);list-style:none;margin:0;padding:0}.delivery li{border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink);border-right:1px solid var(--ink);padding:26px}.delivery li:last-child{border-right:0}.delivery li>span{font:700 8px var(--mono)}.delivery li strong{display:block;font-size:20px;margin:42px 0 11px}.delivery li p{color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;line-height:1.7;margin:0}.docs-link{margin-top:35px}@media(max-width:700px){.hero-actions{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}.starter-grid,.ownership{grid-template-columns:1fr}.ownership>div+div{border-left:0;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}.delivery ol{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.delivery li:nth-child(2){border-right:0}}</style>
